WEBVTT

00:02:57.671 --> 00:03:00.995
led four men in a plot to bomb 
synagogues in the Bronx.

00:03:01.575 --> 00:03:03.526
The lead defendant was James Cromitie,

00:03:03.526 --> 00:03:06.476
a broke Walmart employee
with a history of mental problems.

00:03:06.476 --> 00:03:09.201
And the informant had offered 
him 250,000 dollars

00:03:09.201 --> 00:03:11.587
if he participated in that plot.

00:03:11.587 --> 00:03:14.232
There are many more examples.

00:03:14.232 --> 00:03:16.350
Today, The Intercept
published my new story

00:03:16.350 --> 00:03:20.065
about a counterterrorism sting in Tampa
involving Sami Osmakac,

00:03:20.065 --> 00:03:23.218
a young man who was living 
near Tampa, Florida.

00:03:23.218 --> 00:03:25.890
Osmakac also had 
schizoaffective disorder.

00:03:25.890 --> 00:03:26.895
He too was broke,

00:03:26.895 --> 00:03:29.932
and he had no connections to 
international terrorist groups.

